Anthony Mangano https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anthony_Mangano 0 Anthony Mangano is an Italian-American actor. He has guest starred in a number of notable television series including Diff'rent Strokes, Who's the Boss?, 227, Charles in Charge, Step by Step, Murder, She Wrote, Party of Five, Spin City, Seinfeld and The Wire. He also appeared recurringly on NYPD Blue, Law Order, Rescue Me, Blue Bloods, Public Morals, Law Order: Special Victims Unit and Person of Interest.Mangano has also appeared in the films Point Break, 8 Heads in a Duffel Bag, Raising Helen, Inside Man, The Family, Lost Cat Corona and The Dictator, and in video games The Warriors, Grand Theft Auto IV, Manhunt 2, Need for Speed: Undercover and Grand Theft Auto: The Lost and Damned.
